ogic/labels/area:diagnostics","name":"area:diagnostics","color":"1d76db","default":false,"description":"Phase A: parser/eval errors, REPL, traces"},{"id":10795985541,"node_id":"LA_kwDOP9nMvc8AAAACg32qhQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-foundation/relative-meta-logic/labels/phase:A","name":"phase:A","color":"fbca04","default":false,"description":"Phase A: diagnostics and developer experience"}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2026-04-26T20:32:03Z","updated_at":"2026-04-26T20:33:32Z","closed_at":null,"assignee":null,"author_association":"MEMBER","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Motivation\nWithout a step-by-step trace it is impossible to teach the engine, debug operator-redefinition pitfalls, or build a derivation tree later.\n\n## Goal\n`--trace` flag prints every reduction step, operator resolution, and assignment lookup with span info.\n\n## LiNo Surface\n```\n$ rml --trace demo.lino\n[span demo.lino:3:1] resolve (and: avg)\n[span demo.lino:5:1] eval (a = a) → assigned 1\n```\n\n## API Surface\nCLI flag `--trace` in both `js/` and `rust/` runners; library-level option `trace: true`.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Trace output is reproducible (no nondeterminism).\n- [ ] Tests verify trace lines for representative programs.\n- [ ] Documented in `docs/DIAGNOSTICS.md`.\n\n## References\n- Source case study: [`docs/case-studies/issue-26/`](https://github.com/link-foundation/relative-meta-logic/tree/main/docs/case-studies/issue-26)\n- Comparison docs: [CONCEPTS-COMPARISION.md](https://github.com/link-foundation/relative-meta-logic/blob/main/docs/CONCEPTS-COMPARISION.md), [FEATURE-COMPARISION.md](https://github.com/link-foundation/relative-meta-logic/blob/main/docs/FEATURE-COMPARISION.md)\n- Planning issue: #26\n\n## Dependencies\n- Depends on: #28\n- Blocks: #35\n\n## Out of Scope\nTime-travel debugging or step-back; trace-driven proof export (planned for phase C).\n\n---\n_Plan ID: **A3**, phase **A**. Filed automatically from the case study under `docs/case-studies/issue-26/issue-plan.md` (PR #27)._","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-foundation/relative-meta-logic/issues/30/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-foundation/relative-meta-logic/issues/30/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null,"pinned_comment":null}{"id":1071238333,"node_id":"R_kgDOP9nMvQ","name":"relative-meta-logic","full_name":"link-foundation/relative-meta-logic","private":false,"owner":{"login":"link-foundation","id":176174013,"node_id":"O_kgDOCoAzvQ","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/176174013?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation","html_url":"https://github.com/link-foundation","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/link-foundation/received_events","type":"Organization","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"html_url":"https://github.com/link-foundation/relative-meta-logic","description":"A prototype for logic framework that can reason about anything relative to